headline.main: EU Condemns Launch of NKorea Ballistic Missiles
headline.print_headline: EU Condemns Launch of NKorea Ballistic Missiles

lead_paragraph: The European Union has condemned North Korea for firing four banned ballistic missiles and said it would consult with Japan and international partners on how to react.
